---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Lash, Brow & Body Treatments – Bliss Dermacare" description="Lash extensions, lash lift, brow lamination, body waxing, Brazilian wax, scalp therapy, airbrush spray tan & more at Bliss Dermacare in Tampa, FL.">

  <section class="py-14 bg-[#faf9f7] border-b border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-4">
        <a href="/services/" class="hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">All Services</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Lash, Brow &amp; Body</span>
      </div>
      <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4 block">Lash · Brow · Body · Tan</span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-4">Lash, Brow &amp; Body</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 max-w-xl mx-auto">From lash extensions and brow lamination to body waxing and airbrush spray tans — treatments that keep you looking polished, effortlessly.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">

      <!-- Featured: Spray Tan -->
      <div class="mb-8 group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-amber-200 hover:border-amber-400 relative">
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-10"><span class="bg-amber-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">NEW</span></div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[5fr_7fr]">
          <div class="relative h-56 md:h-auto overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/spray-tan-service.jpg" alt="Custom Airbrush Spray Tan at Bliss Dermacare" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Custom Airbrush Spray Tan</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4 max-w-lg">Look sun-kissed without the UV damage. Our professional airbrush spray tan uses a premium, vegan DHA solution matched to your natural skin tone for a streak-free, natural-looking bronze that develops in 4–6 hours and lasts 7–10 days.</p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-2 mb-5">
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Custom shade matching (light to ultra dark)</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Vegan, paraben-free, alcohol-free DHA</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Results last 7–10 days with proper aftercare</li>
              </ul>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Barrier cream on palms, nails &amp; hairline</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Quick-dry — back to your day in minutes</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Prep instructions &amp; aftercare tips included</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 flex-wrap">
              <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$65</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">30–45 minutes</p></div>
              <a href="/book/" data-service-id="spray-tan" class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-amber-500 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-amber-600 transition-colors shadow-md">Book Now</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 3-col grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300 relative">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-10"><span class="bg-rose-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">TRENDING</span></div>
          <div class="relative h-44 overflow-hidden"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5178001/pexels-photo-5178001.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="Lash Lift & Brow Lamination" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Lash Lift &amp; Brow Lamination</h3><p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Wake up with lifted lashes &amp; sculpted brows — no mascara needed. Tint included. Lasts 6–8 weeks.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$79</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">60 minutes</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="lash-lift-brow-lamination" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-44 overflow-hidden"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5128234/pexels-photo-5128234.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="Lash Extensions" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Lash Extensions</h3><p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Full sets in classic, hybrid, volume &amp; mega volume. Wake up beautiful — zero effort.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$159</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">2 hr | Fills $43</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="lash-extensions" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-44 overflow-hidden"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3997993/pexels-photo-3997993.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="Body & Face Waxing" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Body &amp; Face Waxing</h3><p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Silky-smooth results for face, arms, legs &amp; underarms. Long-lasting &amp; gentle on skin. Age 21+.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$65</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">45–60 min</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="body-and-face-waxing" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-44 overflow-hidden"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/liaison-inc/image/upload/f_auto/q_auto,w_1200/v1762764980/content/thervo/thervo-brazilian-wax-cost-beautician-applying-wax-on-client-as-part-of-hair-removal-treatment.jpg" alt="Brazilian Wax" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Brazilian Wax</h3><p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Complete bikini area removal with precision wax. Beach-ready results that last 3–4 weeks. Age 21+.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$87</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">45–60 min</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="brazilian-wax" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10 bg-neutral-50 border-t border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-400 mb-4">Also Explore</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/services/facials/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Facials</a>
        <a href="/services/advanced-treatments/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Advanced Treatments</a>
        <a href="/services/semipermanent-makeup/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Semipermanent Makeup</a>
        <a href="/services/packages/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Seasonal Packages</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 bg-neutral-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-4">Ready to book?</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-8">Choose your service and request a time that works for you. We'll confirm within 24 hours.</p>
      <a href="/book/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-all font-medium shadow-lg">Request Booking <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/></svg></a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
